{"tid":1385100,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【超緊急】8月5號全港大罷工！唔夠時間啦！香港需要每一個你！","createTime":"2019-07-30T04:04:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T03:40:16.000Z","uid":193032,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"17e3502671f59a26f874f380c986d586d3154bc0","tid":1385100,"uid":193032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:04:34.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">得番六日！！！！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n得番六日時間有幾少大家究竟知唔知！！！！今次真係直接影響香港命運！前線已經為左香港all in， 唔可以白癈佢地嘅血汗。罷工係依場運動入面最緊要嘅一日！係主線中嘅主線，大佬中嘅大佬！<br />\n<br />\n但係依家個個去晒打支線！！！！！全部番黎打大佬啦喂！！<br />\n<br />\n我地要製造到成個社會萬眾一心嘅環境同效果，為每一個香港人加一點衝動同決心就得。簡單黎講的<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<strong>我地要做到嘅係一場有史以來最大嘅罷工廣告campaign</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>鍵盤戰士：</strong></span><br />\n唔好再講推，試下講<br />\n<br />\n「8月5號我會罷工」<br />\n<br />\n「You may say that I&rsquo;m a 罷工er<br />\nBut I&rsquo;m not the only one」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>係人都得：</strong></span><br />\n用word整張無限重複《8月5號我會罷工》嘅A4紙，剪做一條一條，加張膠紙，去至邊痴到邊，搭車又痴，食嘢又痴，行街又痴，特別係𨋢個關門制，一日成棟大厦出入嘅人都會見到！總之要做到無所不在。<br />\n<br />\n屋企大厦嘅信箱都係一個好地方。高級住宅更加有可能接觸到管理層！<br />\n<br />\n有貼紙更好！<br />\n<br />\n依家開始做！唔好再等！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>連儂牆/隧道:</strong></span><br />\n集中重點宣傳番8月5號先！啲狗官遲啲先鬧啦！救番香港之後先有得追究佢地啊！寫張「8月5號我會罷工」都好啊！<br />\n <br />\n要真係比大家知！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>You may say that I&rsquo;m a 罷工er<br />\nBut I&rsquo;m not the only one</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>各大政府合署/大樓/商厦：</strong></span><br />\n其實大家都知公務員入面都有好多人支持五大訴求！不過要佢地罷工，真係要比啲決心、勇氣加一點衝動比佢地！<br />\n<br />\n要係佢地番工時間，放lunch，收工嘅時候，派傳單，同佢地講，香港真係好需要你地放一日假！求各巴絲提供政府部門list同番工，lunch，放工時間。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>金融業：</strong></span><br />\n香港命脈，其實成日示威遊行成日係果邊搞，佢地都好多人知咩事，如果真係令到佢地罷一日，香港有救。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>各大小食肆：</strong></span><br />\nFB有留言功能，大家留番個8月5號我會罷工嘅言，其實唔難，至少比啲壓力管理層。派下poster比舖頭。<br />\n<br />\n街舖罷真係最有畫面<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>地鐵車長：</strong></span><br />\n見到就同佢講聲支持罷工啦，真係香港需要你！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n求大家繼續集思廣益，真係出街做文宣！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<strong>我地要做到一場有史以來最大嘅全港大罷工</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山，多你一分力就係多！真係出力啦！等幾時啊仲？出街痴嘢，派嘢啦！"},{"pid":"52437084d1d155b416c545180d090fa65aa5b8d7","tid":1385100,"uid":193032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:16:53.000Z","msg":"8月5號我會罷工"},{"pid":"0a08afe941e74fa3aa5f9392131625f93e7824bb","tid":1385100,"uid":13514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T04:21:52.000Z","msg":"好"},{"pid":"6c528597c1f2d33e5a8578318542939d64ebed14","tid":1385100,"uid":193032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:50:14.000Z","msg":"8月5號我會罷工"},{"pid":"252c17bb5287fb891618d38011e08d232fdda5d9","tid":1385100,"uid":193032,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:53:46.000Z","msg":"8月5號我會罷工"},{"pid":"04402ae23409a014627a5e9fe086978bf3dfe9f2","tid":1385100,"uid":193032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:21:30.000Z","msg":"8月5號我會罷工<br />\n推"},{"pid":"f3c31eb89236b21b15bb1b8915726d78adcddd4a","tid":1385100,"uid":169938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:21:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5ad6c065f71495e1569ba1e8345093ca4bce0ddb","tid":1385100,"uid":260078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:22:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c856c8b4ca42eefdd3d2f6d4e3ef33514410b14","tid":1385100,"uid":260078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:22:21.000Z","msg":"8月5號我會罷工"},{"pid":"a62ac6fb170acd1afae55f6769b74c648a68132c","tid":1385100,"uid":165997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:25:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a3f3c8c4203ba1fc2f2c58e8b5fc583ac74e610","tid":1385100,"uid":86741,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:26:15.000Z","msg":"由於已經有人發起2/8公務員集會+5/8全港罷工，我地要諗下點先可以maximize 到兩日都join嘅人數，有見罷工同日有七區集會，我建議由<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">今晚開始集中喺呢七區嘅政府合署做文宣+起連儂牆，由門口、地下大堂、𨋢口直至每一層樓嘅office都要貼爆佢。政府合署係開放比所有市民，尤其係啲開放比市民交申請/參加活動嘅部門辦事處（e.g 康文、運輸、社署）更加要貼爆佢。</span></span>要喺呢個星期內令返工嘅公務員都睇到文宣，潛移默化佢地一定要出席<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">2/8嘅集會</span></span>，先有機會搞得成<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">5/8嘅罷工</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n行動時間：<br />\n政府合署內：建議每晚8-10pm<br />\n政府合署門口：10pm後<br />\n原因係可以make sure 班公務員第2朝返工一定睇到，佢working hour 清我地夜晚再貼，亦避免同藍絲公務員正面衝突，強調撕一貼十。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人數：3-5人成團<br />\n<br />\n貼嘅內容：<br />\n主力貼2/8集會同5/8罷工文宣，建議要吸納公務員入面嘅游離分子。貼黑警濫暴。好多中立/藍絲公務員淨係睇港人港地呢啲維穩page，根本冇睇過其他媒體。動之以情：拉攏有子女嘅舊制公務員，你安穩姐，你想唔想你兩腳一伸之後仔女面對地獄般嘅生活？貼新疆慘況逼佢地面對。<br />\n<br />\n以下係七區政府合署地址（from google)：<br />\n<br />\n屯門政府合署：屯喜路1號屯門政府合署<br />\n<br />\n荃灣政府合署：荃灣西樓角路38號<br />\n<br />\n大埔政府合署：新界大埔汀角路1號<br />\n<br />\n沙田政府合署：香港新界沙田上禾輋路1號<br />\n<br />\n旺角政府合署：香港九龍旺角聯運街30號<br />\n<br />\n黃大仙民政諮詢中心：九龍黃大仙龍翔道 138 號龍翔辦公大樓 2 樓 201室<br />\n<br />\n金鐘（直接貼政總）：香港島金鐘添馬添美道2號<br />\n<br />\n希望大家理解好多公務員唔肯行多一步都係受朋輩/老闆壓力，如果可以<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">凝造到一個氣氛，知道有幾多同路人，佢地都會夠膽企出嚟。</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n（緊急）想8月5罷工成功，即刻去政府合署做文宣+連儂化<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1380302\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1380302</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7e11b2ffe753d5dfce82cf81bc05feb5eea64b45","tid":1385100,"uid":193032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:49:00.000Z","msg":"8月5號我會罷工<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"205fcecfd67dcbadd6193eed38ccf1605cf060be","tid":1385100,"uid":193032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:50:58.000Z","msg":"8月5號我會罷工<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76c925a0209826851cf0a30e4cda69e1ecdcdd5b","tid":1385100,"uid":193032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:53:57.000Z","msg":"8月5號我會罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6585c0badec51b49eb02ea70d850b5faac53cd70","tid":1385100,"uid":193032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:54:43.000Z","msg":"8月5號我會罷工<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"